WEBVTT

00:00:00.585 --> 00:00:01.507
UNK

00:00:01.834 --> 00:00:03.785
LEYA TSALZON.

00:00:03.876 --> 00:00:05.118
SHYAULYAY.

00:00:05.293 --> 00:00:06.434
LITVA.

00:00:06.728 --> 00:00:07.746
CHAST'

00:00:07.746 --> 00:00:08.848
TRETYA.

00:00:11.436 --> 00:00:15.210
itster dertseylt mir, az ir zayt gekumen tsurik in Kuzh,

00:00:15.908 --> 00:00:17.927
zaynen shoyn di rusn geven in Kuzh?

00:00:19.097 --> 00:00:19.884
yo.

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:23.006
 zayt ir shoyn geven a bafrayte?

00:00:22.860 --> 00:00:27.511
ikh bin geven a bafrayte. hob ikh geha-, gehat, bin ikh gekumen in Shavl.

00:00:27.484 --> 00:00:28.490
glaykh?

00:00:28.497 --> 00:00:32.035
nu glaykh UNK bin ikh gekumen, geforn in Shavl, zen vos do tut zikh.

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:34.059
ir hot zikh gezegnt mit Kaušienėn?

00:00:34.167 --> 00:00:35.865
Kaušienė iz geforn mit mir.

00:00:35.753 --> 00:00:36.810
in Shavl?

00:00:36.377 --> 00:00:37.113
ye.

00:00:37.086 --> 00:00:38.987
un Kaušienės kinder?

00:00:39.769 --> 00:00:41.585
di gantse mishpokhe, ye?

00:00:42.081 --> 00:00:44.117
tsu vemen zayt ir gekumen in Shavl?

00:00:44.190 --> 00:00:48.048
ikh hob zikh ge- ge- gezukht a a tsimerl, un ikh hob gekrogn...

00:00:48.679 --> 00:00:53.482
un hobn mir ale gelebt tsuzamen tsaytvaylik. nokh dem hot zi zikh avekgeshtelt a shtibl.

00:00:53.269 --> 00:00:54.106
vu?

00:00:54.383 --> 00:00:55.575
do in Shavl.

00:00:55.497 --> 00:00:57.701
iz Kaušienė iz avek fun der erd?

00:00:57.859 --> 00:00:58.916
fun dorf?

00:00:59.142 --> 00:01:04.553
yo, vos zi hot gehat tsu ton shoyn in dorf. der man iz ⟨itst⟩ dershosn, mit tsvey kinder, mit a mamen...

00:01:04.828 --> 00:01:07.505
iz zi avek do, un zi hot genumen do arbetn.

00:01:07.393 --> 00:01:09.344
vu, vu hot zi genumen arbetn?

00:01:09.283 --> 00:01:11.521
nu, kern di gasn UNK

00:01:12.068 --> 00:01:16.297
UNK gehat vos zi hot gekent ton, a bisl hot zi gekent neyen...

00:01:16.185 --> 00:01:19.739
vos hot ir geton, ot in di ershte teg nokh der milkhome in Shavl?

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:21.798
keyn zakh nit.

00:01:21.990 --> 00:01:25.109
ikh hob gehat bakante, fleg ikh avekgeyn un zayn b-

00:01:25.109 --> 00:01:27.671
biz ikh hob zikh bakent mit mayn man.

00:01:28.538 --> 00:01:30.759
nu, hot er genumen arbetn.

00:01:31.170 --> 00:01:33.307
un ot azoy lebn mir di gantse...

00:01:32.453 --> 00:01:36.902
zogt mir, ir hot gehat bakante. dos zenen geven bakante yidn tsu bakante litviner?

00:01:36.452 --> 00:01:37.863
litviner.

00:01:38.207 --> 00:01:42.808
ot di zelbike ale bakante zaynen UNK, UNK zey zikh gedreyt alts dortn.

00:01:42.358 --> 00:01:44.832
un di familye Petrošius iz nokh geven?

00:01:44.721 --> 00:01:46.335
ye, er iz nokh geven.

00:01:46.763 --> 00:01:48.546
un ir flegt bay zey araynkumen?

00:01:48.619 --> 00:01:49.592
ye.

00:01:50.323 --> 00:01:53.979
un ver hot aykh gegebn esn? di bakante flegn aykh gebn esn?

00:01:53.513 --> 00:01:57.270
ye, bakante. nokh dem hob ikh zikh dervust fun Gershon

00:01:57.732 --> 00:01:59.686
vi ge-, az

00:01:59.686 --> 00:02:02.046
di brider zaynen do in Amerike.

00:02:01.866 --> 00:02:03.092
ayere brider?

00:02:02.929 --> 00:02:06.298
ye, tsvey. di iberike zaynen shoyn keyner nit geven.

00:02:06.574 --> 00:02:08.643
nu, ⟨freg ikh⟩ zey, shoyn nemen shikn...

00:02:08.481 --> 00:02:12.255
vi vi iz di nemen fun ayere brider velkhe zaynen in Amerike?

00:02:12.514 --> 00:02:14.111
Velve Ment.

00:02:14.455 --> 00:02:15.968
dos iz geven eyner?

00:02:16.075 --> 00:02:17.503
Un Moyshe Ment.

00:02:18.387 --> 00:02:20.254
Velvl un Moyshe Ment?

00:02:19.770 --> 00:02:22.244
ye. ober zey zaynen shoyn beyde nito.

00:02:25.305 --> 00:02:26.497
zogt mir,

00:02:27.921 --> 00:02:31.644
tsu di froy Lunskienė flegt ir tsugeyn?

00:02:31.245 --> 00:02:33.697
ye, dortn fleg ikh oft zayn.

00:02:33.068 --> 00:02:34.715
nokh di milkhome oykhet?

00:02:33.697 --> 00:02:37.736
ye, zey flegn kumen bay mir un oft flegn zey zayn.

00:02:37.405 --> 00:02:41.364
un ir hot gehat a tsimerl in Shavl tsu... vu hot ir gelebt?

00:02:41.455 --> 00:02:42.934
oyf Vilner gas.

00:02:42.822 --> 00:02:45.870
un ts- vos hot ir gehat, a tsimerl, a dire?

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:47.085
a tsimerl, a tsimerl.

00:02:46.905 --> 00:02:48.958
dos iz geven a melukhishe tsimerl?

00:02:48.610 --> 00:02:49.532
neyn.

00:02:49.656 --> 00:02:51.067
bayn a bakante.

00:02:50.955 --> 00:02:52.619
a yidishe tsu a litvishe?

00:02:52.002 --> 00:02:53.059
a litvishe.

00:02:53.166 --> 00:02:55.168
ir hot ir getsolt dire-gelt?

00:02:54.735 --> 00:02:55.606
ye.

00:02:55.815 --> 00:02:58.765
un vos hot ir... ir hot nokh nit gearbet dan?

00:02:58.127 --> 00:02:59.235
neyn.

00:02:58.765 --> 00:03:02.559
ver hot aykh gegebn gelt oyf tsu tsoln, oyf tsu koyfn a bisl shpayz?

00:03:02.430 --> 00:03:06.339
ikh fleg shoyn krign fun di brider zakh, ikh fleg farkoyfn.

00:03:06.852 --> 00:03:10.035
glaykh flegt ir on- onnemen fun di brider krign zakhn?

00:03:08.674 --> 00:03:10.392
ye, s'iz shoyn gekumen in

00:03:10.392 --> 00:03:12.881
in a shtetl, hot ir efsher gehert, Naynshtot.

00:03:12.775 --> 00:03:13.798
yo?

00:03:13.809 --> 00:03:18.270
nu, iz gekumen eyner, zogt er: "s'iz do dayne tsvey brider, yene zaynen umgekumen".

00:03:18.394 --> 00:03:20.447
un er iz gekumen tsu aykh in Shavl?

00:03:20.402 --> 00:03:22.184
ye, ye, der,

00:03:22.663 --> 00:03:23.754
der,

00:03:24.418 --> 00:03:28.361
der Shvekshner iz gekumen in in Shavl, ye, in Shavl.

00:03:28.418 --> 00:03:30.538
zogt er: "dayne brider zaynen do".

00:03:31.253 --> 00:03:32.287
heyst es.

00:03:32.287 --> 00:03:33.519
nu, zogt er

00:03:33.519 --> 00:03:36.849
"UNK ober zey zaynen geblibn in Amerike, zaynen nit geforn."

00:03:36.822 --> 00:03:38.672
un er iz aleyn gekumen tsurik?

00:03:38.948 --> 00:03:42.452
er iz gekumen tsurik, veys ikh nit, nokh dem hob ikh UNK azoy nit getrofn mer.

00:03:42.154 --> 00:03:43.813
dem yidn hot ir nisht getrofn?

00:03:43.813 --> 00:03:46.620
efsher gedenkt ir vi iz geven di familye-nomen fun dem yid?

00:03:45.613 --> 00:03:47.328
neyn, neyn, ikh gedenk nit...

00:03:46.660 --> 00:03:47.719
ir gedenkt nit.

00:03:47.719 --> 00:03:50.787
nor er, er hot aykh opgegebn a gerus fun ayere brider.

00:03:49.528 --> 00:03:52.779
ye, zey UNK zog ikh: "az du shraybst",

00:03:53.038 --> 00:04:00.102
zog ikh: "gib mir dem adres". git mir. tomer gegebn dem adres, hob ikh ongeshribn, un glaykh hobn zey genumen shikn, glaykh.

00:04:00.987 --> 00:04:04.592
zey hobn gevolt ikh zol kumen ober ikh bin geven in gantsn tsetumlt.

00:04:05.374 --> 00:04:06.602
az ikh hob UNK

00:04:06.602 --> 00:04:09.336
nit gevolt zol ikh itst oyf vayter gey⟨UNK⟩

00:04:09.336 --> 00:04:11.763
rizikirn dem grenets.

00:04:11.787 --> 00:04:15.291
vayter in Poyln zaynen ale gelofn, zaynen a sakh durkhgefaln.

00:04:15.297 --> 00:04:17.248
UNK ikh hob dos oyf UNK keyn koyekh nit.

00:04:17.355 --> 00:04:19.694
un azoy hot ir farblibn in Shavl?

00:04:19.802 --> 00:04:20.761
UNK khasene gehat

00:04:20.761 --> 00:04:21.467
mit mayn man.

00:04:21.067 --> 00:04:25.112
in, mit velkhe umshtandn hot ir zikh bakant mit a-

00:04:24.122 --> 00:04:25.972
eyner hot undz bakent.

00:04:25.945 --> 00:04:26.816
ver?

00:04:26.890 --> 00:04:28.234
eyner a yid.

00:04:28.628 --> 00:04:29.871
a yid, yo?

00:04:28.628 --> 00:04:30.276
yo.

00:04:31.648 --> 00:04:35.186
fargesn zayn familye, Markus, Markus.

00:04:34.770 --> 00:04:37.396
a yid vos iz zayn familye-nomen iz geven Markus?

00:04:36.660 --> 00:04:38.105
Markus, ye.

00:04:37.673 --> 00:04:42.831
un fun vanet iz er aleyn geven? er hot durkhgelebt di milkhome in geto tsu in Rusland iz er geven?

00:04:42.111 --> 00:04:44.417
ikh veys nit, in geto iz er geven.

00:04:43.900 --> 00:04:46.071
Markus iz geven oykhet in geto, ye?

00:04:44.490 --> 00:04:45.834
ye.

00:04:47.173 --> 00:04:49.833
un, er hot aykh bakent mit ayer...

00:04:49.637 --> 00:04:50.812
mit mayn man.

00:04:50.430 --> 00:04:51.656
mit ayer man.

00:04:52.540 --> 00:04:53.844
un,

00:04:53.844 --> 00:04:55.852
un ir hot khasene gehat mit im, ye?

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:56.094
ye.

00:04:55.852 --> 00:04:58.321
ir gedenkt dem yor ven ir hot khasene gehat?

00:04:59.644 --> 00:05:05.206
nu glaykh in finf un fertsikstn yor zaynen mir tsuzamengekumen lebn, in finf un fertsiktn yor...

00:05:04.470 --> 00:05:06.674
dos iz geven zeyer gikh.

00:05:05.432 --> 00:05:08.851
nay yor azoy zaynen mir bay Jonasn gepravet.

00:05:09.381 --> 00:05:10.742
oykh bay Jonas.

00:05:10.512 --> 00:05:13.611
bay Jonasn, dos iz bay, bay Petrošiusn?

00:05:13.363 --> 00:05:14.352
ye.

00:05:14.207 --> 00:05:17.272
hot ir gepravet ayer ayer khasene, ye?

00:05:16.485 --> 00:05:18.183
UNK far a khasene geven.

00:05:18.510 --> 00:05:20.816
ovntbroyt hot men gemakht un fartik.

00:05:20.957 --> 00:05:24.579
un ir hot zikh opgeshribn in a, in a sovetishn antshtalt?

00:05:26.290 --> 00:05:28.461
un nokh der khasene hot ir gearbet?

00:05:28.635 --> 00:05:29.456
neyn.

00:05:29.462 --> 00:05:31.177
ir hot keyn mol nisht gearbet?

00:05:30.643 --> 00:05:31.447
neyn.

00:05:32.027 --> 00:05:34.974
mayn man hot gearbet in fabrik.

00:05:34.508 --> 00:05:36.257
un er hot aykh oysgehaltn?

00:05:35.807 --> 00:05:36.763
ye.

00:05:37.326 --> 00:05:39.902
un kinder hot ir a sakh?

00:05:39.756 --> 00:05:42.669
tsvey, a yingl mit a meydl.

00:05:41.410 --> 00:05:43.648
vi z-, vi zaynen zeyere nemen oykh?

00:05:43.553 --> 00:05:44.711
Benhard...

00:05:44.886 --> 00:05:45.963
Benhard?

00:05:44.937 --> 00:05:46.180
Tsalzon.

00:05:45.963 --> 00:05:47.546
Benhard iz der zun?

00:05:47.485 --> 00:05:49.943
Ye, un Judita Tsalzon.

00:05:50.134 --> 00:05:52.288
Itster iz zi shoyn Vaičiulienė.

00:05:52.429 --> 00:05:54.886
ye, loytn man.

00:05:52.682 --> 00:05:53.823
loyt man?

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:58.042
un eyniklekh hot ir a sakh?

00:05:57.930 --> 00:06:02.058
tsvey, der zun hot a zun un di tokhter hot a tokhter.

00:06:02.689 --> 00:06:04.927
der zun lebt oykh in Shavl?

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:06.598
neyn, in Meml lebt er.

00:06:07.667 --> 00:06:10.175
der zun bazukht aykh oft?

00:06:10.182 --> 00:06:12.690
nu nit keyn sakh, er hot nit keyn tsayt.

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:15.271
UNK ni- nit oft kumt er.

00:06:15.447 --> 00:06:17.854
un ir, ir fort tsu im oykhet nisht?

00:06:18.315 --> 00:06:19.338
nu, UNK

00:06:19.412 --> 00:06:23.827
itster bin ikh gelegn in bolnitse dortn in Meml, in roytn kreyts.

00:06:23.732 --> 00:06:26.240
vos iz aykh, vos hot mit aykh pasirt?

00:06:26.331 --> 00:06:27.618
nu, iz shoyn bay mir

00:06:27.618 --> 00:06:29.295
a ernster krankeyt.

00:06:31.697 --> 00:06:34.425
un dortn iz mir nokh erger gevorn UNK.

00:06:35.123 --> 00:06:39.184
vayzt oys, hobn zey nisht gemakht keyn analize oyf der refues, ken men gebn.

00:06:39.730 --> 00:06:42.542
vayle ikh zol dortn zeyer ge- shlekht gefilt.

00:06:42.683 --> 00:06:45.141
zey hobn shoyn nit geklert az ikh vel blaybn lebn.

00:06:46.142 --> 00:06:47.047
UNK

00:06:47.290 --> 00:06:50.304
un di tokhter lebt bay aykh in, in Shavl?

00:06:49.821 --> 00:06:54.827
PIETINIAM RAJONE lebt zi. yo, dortn in PIETINIAM.

00:06:51.272 --> 00:06:53.476
dos iz a doremdike rayon, ye?

00:06:55.575 --> 00:06:58.606
un an, a di tokhter lebt tsuzamen mit an eynikl?

00:06:58.174 --> 00:07:01.644
neyn, di tokhter, der eynikl hot a UNK dire.

00:07:02.140 --> 00:07:04.547
der eynikl hot bay aykh, iz shoyn oykhet khasene gehat?

00:07:03.523 --> 00:07:04.934
neyn.

00:07:04.789 --> 00:07:06.487
neyn. ober zi lebt bazunder?

00:07:05.970 --> 00:07:07.432
ye, bazunder.

00:07:07.152 --> 00:07:11.432
di tokhter mit di eyniklekh, zey, mit di UNK, zey bazukhn aykh oft?

00:07:11.488 --> 00:07:12.984
yo, zey kumen,

00:07:13.125 --> 00:07:14.536
zey kumen tsu ⟨gast⟩.

00:07:18.238 --> 00:07:22.889
gut, ikh dank aykh zeyer efsh-, efsh-, far a groys, far aza sheynem intervyu.

00:07:19.622 --> 00:07:20.746
nu gut.

00:07:22.947 --> 00:07:28.881
un ikh vintsh aykh ir zolt hobn nakhes fun ayer zun mit ayer tokhter mit ayere eyniklekh!

00:07:25.798 --> 00:07:27.159
a dank aykh.

00:07:28.583 --> 00:07:30.382
a groysn dank aykh.

00:07:35.704 --> 00:07:36.643
nu,

00:07:36.784 --> 00:07:39.309
dem bild iz fun di mamen.

00:07:39.467 --> 00:07:41.891
vi hot ge-, vi iz geven der nomen fun ayer muter?

00:07:41.796 --> 00:07:43.224
Yu-, Yudis.

00:07:43.703 --> 00:07:45.620
Yudis, Yudis Ment.

00:07:43.770 --> 00:07:45.249
Ment.

00:07:47.533 --> 00:07:50.075
 in vifltn yor iz gemakht gevorn der bild?

00:07:52.191 --> 00:07:53.568
tsvey un draysiktn UNK.

00:07:53.862 --> 00:07:56.134
vu hot men dos fotografirt?

00:07:55.819 --> 00:07:56.842
in Meml.

00:07:56.832 --> 00:07:59.121
dos iz a, di muter iz geven bay aykh tsu gast?

00:07:58.688 --> 00:07:59.509
ye.

00:08:00.831 --> 00:08:04.875
un vi hot ir, vi hot ir bakumen, vi hot zikh oysgehit der bild?

00:08:05.151 --> 00:08:08.165
nu iz UNK iz geven, ikh hob tsu khaveyrim bahaltn.

00:08:08.121 --> 00:08:09.667
ir hot oysbahaltn?

00:08:09.285 --> 00:08:12.890
yo, a kleynem bildele. nokh dem hob ikh do gegebn fargresern.

00:08:12.306 --> 00:08:15.405
ober fun vanet hot ir gekumen, bakumen dem kleynem bildl?

00:08:15.276 --> 00:08:17.464
fun, ikh hob gehat bahaltn...

00:08:17.132 --> 00:08:20.399
di, di gantse milkhome hot ir oysgetrogn bay zikh ot dem bildele?

00:08:20.035 --> 00:08:20.974
ye.

00:08:22.212 --> 00:08:23.522
di gantse milkhome?

00:08:23.207 --> 00:08:24.095
ye.

00:08:25.738 --> 00:08:26.964
KOKS DABAR

00:08:27.004 --> 00:08:27.875
dos?

00:08:29.147 --> 00:08:31.233
nu, der bild iz

00:08:31.797 --> 00:08:33.056
mayn zun.

00:08:33.736 --> 00:08:35.582
der ershter fun links, ye?

00:08:34.833 --> 00:08:35.637
ye.

00:08:35.582 --> 00:08:36.988
zayn nomen iz?

00:08:36.792 --> 00:08:38.001
Benhard.

00:08:39.463 --> 00:08:41.420
Benhard Tsal-

00:08:40.486 --> 00:08:41.560
Tsalzon.

00:08:41.420 --> 00:08:43.264
vos er lebt in Meml, ye?

00:08:42.394 --> 00:08:44.261
ye, er lebt in Meml.

00:08:43.962 --> 00:08:45.020
lebn im?

00:08:45.364 --> 00:08:47.484
der tsveyter iz mayn man.

00:08:48.418 --> 00:08:50.167
Nokhim Tsalzon.

00:08:51.068 --> 00:08:52.732
do bin ikh.

00:08:53.025 --> 00:08:56.090
un do iz mayn tokhter,

00:08:56.535 --> 00:08:58.436
mayner an eynikl.

00:08:58.189 --> 00:08:59.870
zey, vos zayn nomen iz?

00:09:00.417 --> 00:09:01.575
Deivis,

00:09:01.767 --> 00:09:03.549
Deivis Calzonas.

00:09:03.657 --> 00:09:04.725
un dos iz

00:09:04.725 --> 00:09:05.945
Elinka

00:09:06.053 --> 00:09:06.941
Shpits.

00:09:06.795 --> 00:09:08.763
un vu iz dos gemakht gevorn?

00:09:09.478 --> 00:09:12.408
vu, vu iz do gemakht gevorn der der bild?

00:09:11.368 --> 00:09:13.269
dem bild hot men gemakht,

00:09:13.343 --> 00:09:16.374
fotografirt in Kuži- in,

00:09:16.583 --> 00:09:17.887
in Shvekshne

00:09:17.887 --> 00:09:22.044
un UNK gemakht hot men in Shavl UNK UNK oysgearbet.

00:09:22.152 --> 00:09:25.352
in vifltn yor iz dos fotografirt, gedenkt ir efsher?

00:09:29.003 --> 00:09:31.056
in zeks un fertsiktn yor.

00:09:31.264 --> 00:09:33.384
az ir hot shoyn do eyniklekh iz...

00:09:32.952 --> 00:09:34.667
neyn nisht UNK,

00:09:37.626 --> 00:09:39.324
gedenk nit, ikh gedenk...

00:09:39.229 --> 00:09:41.602
in vos far a yor, gedenkt ir nit dos?

00:09:40.815 --> 00:09:42.007
neyn.

00:09:46.300 --> 00:09:47.593
der bild,

00:09:48.831 --> 00:09:50.394
der bild iz

00:09:51.075 --> 00:09:53.718
di litvine vu ikh hob zikh oysbahaltn.

00:09:53.758 --> 00:09:56.114
der nomen iz irer Kaušienė.

00:09:55.969 --> 00:09:57.633
un der f- ershter nomen?

00:09:59.142 --> 00:10:00.941
dos iz di familye-nomen, Kauš-

00:09:59.547 --> 00:10:01.802
der familye-nomen, nu...

00:10:01.217 --> 00:10:02.797
un vi zi hot geheysn?

00:10:02.533 --> 00:10:03.843
Teodora.

00:10:04.187 --> 00:10:05.868
zi lebt nokh haynt?

00:10:04.812 --> 00:10:07.002
neyn, zi iz toyt.

00:10:07.002 --> 00:10:09.328
mit fir yor tsurik iz zi geshtorbn.

00:10:09.250 --> 00:10:10.864
vifl yor iz zi dan geven?

00:10:11.562 --> 00:10:13.108
eyn un akhtsik.

00:10:19.847 --> 00:10:21.579
der bild iz

00:10:21.923 --> 00:10:23.976
Kaušienės zun.

00:10:26.631 --> 00:10:27.994
er iz shoyn toyt.

00:10:27.880 --> 00:10:29.072
vi iz zayn nomen?

00:10:28.993 --> 00:10:29.665
Ignas

00:10:29.665 --> 00:10:30.354
Kau⟨UNK⟩as.

00:10:30.765 --> 00:10:32.497
tsi iz shoyn vi er iz toyt?

00:10:32.993 --> 00:10:34.657
nu, es muz shoyn zayn a

00:10:34.832 --> 00:10:36.969
tsvelf yor er iz toyt.

00:10:37.144 --> 00:10:39.129
dos iz der elterer fun Kauš-?

00:10:38.325 --> 00:10:39.973
der yingerer.

00:10:46.982 --> 00:10:49.645
nu dos dos iz a bruder

00:10:49.645 --> 00:10:53.506
fun mir, fun Leye Tsalzon.

00:10:52.990 --> 00:10:55.110
UNK, vi iz zayn nomen?

00:10:54.897 --> 00:10:56.021
Moyshe,

00:10:56.297 --> 00:10:57.674
Moyshe Ment.

00:10:58.407 --> 00:11:01.421
vi vi hot er durkhgelebt UNK di milkhome?

00:11:01.090 --> 00:11:02.839
er iz geven in kontslager.

00:11:02.524 --> 00:11:04.712
in vos far a kontslager veyst ir?

00:11:03.655 --> 00:11:04.898
veys ikh nit.

00:11:06.102 --> 00:11:08.492
un vu gefint er zikh do?

00:11:08.835 --> 00:11:11.883
der bild iz fun Amerike ober er lebt shoyn nit.

00:11:12.649 --> 00:11:14.347
er iz geshtorbn.

00:11:13.611 --> 00:11:15.140
s'iz shoyn lang tsurik?

00:11:14.995 --> 00:11:17.790
yo, s'iz shoyn a tsayt er iz geshtorbn.

00:11:25.896 --> 00:11:27.273
ver iz der mentsh?

00:11:27.128 --> 00:11:31.256
der, dos iz mayner a bruder, mit a zun.

00:11:30.655 --> 00:11:32.758
vi iz dem bruders nomen?

00:11:31.988 --> 00:11:33.720
Velve Ment.

00:11:34.587 --> 00:11:36.235
un der yingele heyst

00:11:36.780 --> 00:11:38.900
Bentsl Ment.

00:11:39.109 --> 00:11:41.111
Bentsl dos iz Velvls a zun?

00:11:41.033 --> 00:11:41.955
ye.

00:11:42.012 --> 00:11:44.048
Vel-, Velves a zun.

00:11:44.155 --> 00:11:46.089
vu iz dos fotografirt gevorn?

00:11:45.555 --> 00:11:47.253
in me-, in Amerike.

00:11:47.462 --> 00:11:49.700
itster lebt nokh ayer bruder?

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:50.139
neyn.

00:11:50.483 --> 00:11:52.316
ir veyst ven iz er geshtorbn?

00:11:51.900 --> 00:11:52.771
neyn.

00:11:52.913 --> 00:11:56.855
nor ikh veys az er iz geshtorbn vayl ikh hob keyne briv nit fun zey.

00:11:56.997 --> 00:11:59.539
vayl er iz geven nit keyn yunger.

00:12:03.088 --> 00:12:04.736
dos iz mayn man.

00:12:07.864 --> 00:12:09.528
der nomen iz?

00:12:09.118 --> 00:12:10.392
der nomen iz

00:12:10.392 --> 00:12:12.195
Nokhim Calzonas.

00:12:14.563 --> 00:12:16.770
itster lebt ir zalbetsveyt mit im?

00:12:16.977 --> 00:12:18.813
ye, itster lebn mir tsuzamen.
